vkontakte-tool (0.6) lucid; urgency=low

  * Fixed crush on invalid login.
  * Show graffiti image size in GUI.
  * Fixed changed regexp for login (LP:591250).
  * Properties panel added.
  * Uploading format is now selectable (LP:565254). Autoselection
    is enabled by default.
  * New nicks authentification is now supported (LP:577104).

 -- Alexey Osipov <lion-simba@pridelands.ru>  Fri, 25 Jun 2010 23:35:04 +0700

vkontakte-tool (0.5) karmic; urgency=low

  * Uploading graffiti as PNG image instead of JPEG gives less
    distortion on the image (LP:457582).
  * PNGs with width of 586 pixels uploaded "as is" without recompress.
  * Various logging to stderr.
  * New login scheme using s-value (LP:474069).
  * No more graffiti autoconfirmation, because of possible captcha. Show link
    to confirmation page instead (LP:501867).

 -- Alexey Osipov <lion-simba@pridelands.ru>  Fri, 08 Jan 2010 21:40:36 +0600

vkontakte-tool (0.4) jaunty; urgency=low

  * More accurate error messages shown if graffiti upload failed.
  * More accurate checking of graffiti upload success (LP:416722).
  * Can now load PNGs with alpha-channel, which is simply ignored.

