vkontakte-tool (0.3) jaunty; urgency=low

  * Connection problems don't crush program, but cause an error message. 
    (Closes: #413269)
  * Failed login cause an explaining error message.
  * Fixed crush on startup on systems having both wxWidgets 2.6 and 2.8
    installed.
  * Deprecation warning at startup removed.
  * Success graffiti upload dialog shows a link to the friend's/group's
    wall page instead of a link to yourself wall page. (Closes: #413260)
  * Graffiti upload success check improved - error dialog shown on fail.
  * Friends/groups lists in GUI part are sorted now.

